# Local-dev config for this repo's deploy / SD-stage / benchmark tools (tools/_devenv.py).
#
# Copy to `.env` (gitignored) and set the paths for your workstation. Committed files
# carry NO absolute local paths — these tools read them from here at runtime.
#
# Every var is OPTIONAL: unset falls back to the sibling-layout default (a checkout of
# each repo next to this one, under a shared parent dir). Set a var only when your
# layout differs. This is a LOCAL-DEV helper — SeedSigner-OS and the production
# MicroPython build assemble their own pieces and do not use these scripts.

# The SeedSigner app checkout root — contains src/seedsigner (the app package we deploy)
# and src/lang-packs (the app's bundled language packs, which we copy to the SD). This
# repo POINTS ONLY AT THE APP: it neither knows the pack repo nor builds packs, so
# src/lang-packs is the pack source. Absent/empty packs there = a valid English-only deploy.
#   default: <this repo's parent>/seedsigner
#SS_APP_DIR=/abs/path/to/seedsigner

# The embit checkout root — contains src/embit.
#   default: <parent>/embit
#SS_EMBIT_DIR=/abs/path/to/embit

# Optional override: point the SD stager at a PRE-BUILT packs dir (<dir>/<locale>/...)
# instead of the app's src/lang-packs. For oddball layouts only; normally leave unset so
# whatever the app bundled is what deploys.
#SS_PACKS_DIR=/abs/path/to/some/prebuilt/lang-packs

# btc-datagen checkout — PSBT fixtures for the cUR benchmarks (tools/device_scan/).
#   default: <parent>/btc-datagen
#SS_BTC_DATAGEN_DIR=/abs/path/to/btc-datagen
